node.text:
//alive jan 19 '21 : 15.38

That place, that day, it was all magical and so, so dreamy, it was a complete different dimension. 
The whole day was already such a ride filled w so many emotions, visiting college after so long, reliving all those emotions and I could see myself doing all those stupid, weird, crazy things, basically I guess I relived my entire first year that day? Haha. 
And then, ah, the highlight ~ dancing and ofc writing (because how can I not?) 
Roamed around the campus while listening to these amazing songs ~ 'Chaudhary', 'Radha kaise na jale', 'Taal se taal mila', 'Barso re', 'Dola re', 'Jiya jale' (my hearttttt<3). 
And I twirled and twirled!

Ahh! It was surreal, and that is why I love to dance! 
Dancing is so liberating. To lose yourself in the beats and align yourself w the energy of universe and dance like a jhalli, ah, like a jogan. It doesn't matter whether the steps match w the beats or anything. It just doesn't, not to me. 
It is just the music and the universe, and me surrendering myself to it! 

I danced, ran, twirled, jumped around the ground and I shouted, "I am alive!".

#uni <33

Mud mud kar, 
Tujhe dekhne lagi hoon.

Teri baaton ko sunne ke lie,
Bebas hone lagi hoon

Tujhse milne ke lie

Roothne ke tujhse

Baaton mai apni
Tera zikar karne lagi hoon

Shayad tujhme ab
Main khone lagi hoon

Main khud se jhooth bolne lagi hoon
Shyad tujhe chahne lagi hoon

//tears 12 Apr :  19.39
I can't cry
I don't know why
But I just can't
These tears will flow
When I'll look at you,
Or when I get those flashbacks
Or when I-I 
They will, 
I don't know why
But in that
Darkroom, when I am lonely
They refuse to come out?
When I give them a chance
To express themselves
They betray me, 
But when I am anywhere near you
They won't just stop
Betraying me again
Is that all I get?
Tears and betrayal?

Feelings are ~ 
Erratic. Weird. Awkward. Crazy. Tiring. Magical. Overwhelming. Jumpy. Unpredictable. Contradictory.  Temporary. Unstable. Fluctuating. Broken. Lost. Messy. Dramatic. Cluttered. Stubborn. Problematic. Scary. Vague. Uncertain. Confusing. Irrational. Sweet. Chaotic. Calm. Loud. Peaceful. Terrific. Divine. Powerful. 
Real. 
Intense. 
And so Human.
